name: VOXELFINE #7: "Woman with an Umbrella" by Marie Bracquemond 3D voxelart model (.glb)
description: I made this one mostly because I wanted to work with the umbrella in voxels. I tried not to be wasteful with space, so I worked with a depth of 10 (instead of 16) and I think it came out well. Voxelfines are collectible 3D voxel models of iconic works of art. They are ready to be imported into a VR or AR experience of your choice. By Lorem Ipsum, 2021.
